From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Patric Stout <github@truebrain.nl>
Date: Sat, 4 Jul 2026 11:46:19 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 05/10] chore: include all required system headers

Linux compilers tend to be more strict in what headers
they need, where other compilers tend to auto-include
some.
